; Tests for commodity.cc: map_prices with CURRENT_TIME() fallback
; Covers: line 79 (when = CURRENT_TIME() when no moment and no epoch)
;         Also exercises prices command which calls map_prices

P 2024/01/01 EUR $1.10
P 2024/06/01 EUR $1.15
P 2024/12/01 EUR $1.20

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses  10 EUR
    Assets

; The prices command calls map_prices with no explicit moment
; which triggers the CURRENT_TIME() fallback at line 79
test prices EUR
2024/01/01 EUR             $1.10
2024/06/01 EUR             $1.15
2024/12/01 EUR             $1.20
end test
